HEADWORD: Ember-goose
<hw>Em"ber-goose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Norw.
<ets>embergaas</ets>, <ets>hav-imber</ets>, <ets>hav-immer</ets>, Icel.
<ets>himbrin</ets>, <ets>himbrimi</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld>
<def>The loon or great northern diver. See <er>Loon</er>.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>emmer-goose</asp> and
<asp>imber-goose</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

